article_id:101,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Lowen's Skill "Winds, Heal Us!"[Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue where Lowen will not use the skill &quot;Winds, Heal Us!&quot; during quests as an AI adventurer in your team.</div><div>This issue occurs regardless of the skill&#39;s level.</div><div><br></div><div>When controlling Lowen, the skill can still be used normally, and its effects are working as intended.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.</div><div>Any further updates regarding this issue will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542865200"></span>]</strong></span><br>This issue was fixed in the data update on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542865200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1542706800,update_time1543215637